:Theme_AuthorityAndLaw a :Theme ;
  :description "Creon asserts political authority through strict civic law."^^xsd:string .

:Theme_BurialEdict a :Theme ;
  :description "The burial prohibition drives interrogation, suspicion, and punishment threats."^^xsd:string .

:Theme_FearAndResponsibility a :Theme ;
  :description "The Guard oscillates between fear, survival, and duty to report."^^xsd:string .

:Theme_CorruptionByMoney a :Theme ;
  :description "Creon links the crime to bribery and the corrupting force of money."^^xsd:string .
